OL,7,FThe Trussell Trust charity says it's
OL,8,Fhelped a record number of people
OL,9,Fthrough food banks in the North West
OL,10,Fover the past year.
OL,12,FIt's as as people on low incomes
OL,13,Fstruggle to afford the essentials.
OL,14,FFigures reveal 300,056 emergency food
OL,15,Fparcels were provided to people facing
OL,16,Fhardship in the North West between
OL,17,FApril 2023 and March 2024 - more than
OL,18,Fever before.
OL,20,FThat's almost a 60 percent increase
OL,21,Fcompared to five years ago.
