OL,7,FNearly 132,000 of these parcels
OL,8,Fprovided for children.
OL,10,FThis is the highest number of parcels
OL,11,Fdistributed in a single year by the
OL,12,Ffood banks in the charity's UK-wide
OL,13,Fnetwork and represents a concerning
OL,14,F58% increase in the total support
OL,15,Fprovided compared to five years ago.
OL,17,FCharlotte Moorcroft, Fundraising
OL,18,FOfficer, North Liverpool Foodbank
OL,19,Fsaid: "More and more households and
OL,20,Ffamilies are finding themselves at
OL,21,Fcrisis point.
