OL,7,F"Over the last year, we saw a
OL,8,Fsignificant increase in the number of
OL,9,Fpeople accessing our foodbanks,
OL,10,Fsupporting people with well over
OL,11,F14,000 emergency food parcels, with
OL,12,F4,913 of these being for children.
OL,14,F"It's heartbreaking to hear the
OL,15,Fstories of those who are in crisis,
OL,16,Fwith so many people unable to afford
OL,17,Fthe basics and needing emergency
OL,18,Fsupport.
OL,20,F"We are here to support everyone who
OL,21,Fneeds us."
