OL,7,FNationally, a record 3.1 million
OL,8,Femergency food parcels have been
OL,9,Fhanded out in just a year.
OL,11,FThe number of people of pension age
OL,12,Fpicking up parcels also increased by
OL,13,F27% to 179,000, according to the
OL,14,Ftrust, with older people who rent said
OL,15,Fto be particularly likely to need help.
