OL,7,FThe trust is warning that the next UK
OL,8,Fgovernment cannot afford to ignore
OL,9,Fthis issue and is urging all political
OL,10,Fleaders to set out how they will build
OL,11,Fa future where no one needs a food
OL,12,Fbank to survive.
OL,14,FIt's calling for urgent reform of the
OL,15,Fsocial security system, so it ensures
OL,16,Feveryone's income covers the cost of
OL,17,Fthe essentials we all need in life.
