OL,7,FEmma Revie, Chief Executive at the
OL,8,FTrussell Trust said: "It's 2024 and
OL,9,Fwe're facing historically high levels
OL,10,Fof food bank need.
OL,12,F"As a society, we cannot allow this to
OL,13,Fcontinue.
OL,15,F"We must not let food banks become the
OL,16,Fnew norm.
