OL,7,F"As we approach the next UK General
OL,8,FElection, we urgently need all
OL,9,Fpolitical leaders to set out how they
OL,10,Fwill build a future where no one needs
OL,11,Fa food bank to survive.
OL,13,F"Voters want to see a change and we
OL,14,Fneed cross-government action at all
OL,15,Flevels to deliver it.
OL,17,F"We know what's pushing people to food
OL,18,Fbanks, so we know what needs to change.
