OL,7,F"A supportive social security system
OL,8,Fis the bedrock on which we end hunger
OL,9,Ffor good.
OL,11,F"Building on this, we need much more
OL,12,Feffective employment and financial
OL,13,Fsupport for parents, carers and
OL,14,Fdisabled people and action to ensure
OL,15,Feveryone can have the security we all
OL,16,Fneed to access opportunities and have
OL,17,Fhope for the future, through more
OL,18,Fsecure and flexible jobs and
OL,19,Finvestment in social housing.
OL,21,F"Food banks are not the answer.
