OL,7,F"They will be there to support people
OL,8,Fas long as they are needed, but our
OL,9,Fpolitical leaders must take bold
OL,10,Faction to build a future where
OL,11,Feveryone has enough money to afford
OL,12,Fthe life's essentials.
OL,14,F"The time to act is now."
OL,16,FThe hope is no one should rely on
OL,17,Fhandouts to survive.
